                    <span class="badge bg-success-soft text-success rounded-pill px-3 py-2 mb-3">Supermarket Solution</span>
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">Supermarket <span class="text-success">POS System</span></h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-4">Streamline your supermarket operations with our comprehensive POS solution designed for retail success.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                        <a href="#demo" class="btn btn-success btn-lg px-4">Request Demo</a>
                        <a href="#features" class="btn btn-outline-success btn-lg px-4">View Features</a>
